{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">= Gameplay =</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">POUMOSA is a Point And Click adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is intended for players who like dialogues, puzzles and wiggling mustaches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396630/extras/Moustache.gif?t=1735467774\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">= Story =</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In 1503, Europe is captivated by the promise of the New World. Expeditions are being prepared in all the kingdoms, each hoping to obtain their share of the riches and unexplored lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play the role of Balthazar De Rochemort, a nobleman who invests in one of these expeditions and boards a ship. However, caught in a violent storm, your expedition drifts and discovers a small mysterious island, inhabited by an unknown people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Study their language !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396630/extras/Journal.jpg?t=1735467774\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover their history !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396630/extras/Temple.jpg?t=1735467774\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Share their culture !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396630/extras/Sleeping.jpg?t=1735467774\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or make your trip profitable...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396630/extras/persuasive.jpg?t=1735467774\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's up to you !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's your investment after all !</p>